Name: Total Athletic Investment
Expression: SUM('Athletic Scholarships by Term 2017-2025'[Amount Awarded])

Name: ROI per Scholarship Dollar
Expression: DIVIDE([Average Career GPA Athletes] * 10000, [Average Scholarship Investment], 0)

Name: Cost per Graduate
Expression: DIVIDE([Total Athletic Investment], [Projected Graduates], 0)

Name: Budget Efficiency Ratio
Expression: DIVIDE(SUM('Athletic Scholarships by Term 2017-2025'[Amount Earned]), SUM('Athletic Scholarships by Term 2017-2025'[Amount Awarded]), 0)

Name: Average Scholarship Investment
Expression: AVERAGE('Scholarship Summary by Term and Sport'[Average Scholarship Amount])

Name: Total Scholarship Athletes
Expression: SUM('Scholarship Summary by Term and Sport'[Total Scholarship Athletes])

Name: Scholarship Coverage Rate
Expression: DIVIDE([Total Scholarship Athletes], [Total Athletes Program], 0) * 100

Name: Financial Risk Score
Expression: 100 - ([Budget Efficiency Ratio] * 100)

Name: Investment per Sport
Expression: DIVIDE([Total Athletic Investment], DISTINCTCOUNT('Participation Summary by Term and Sport'[Sport Name]), 0)

Name: Scholarship Yield Rate
Expression: DIVIDE(SUM('Athletic Scholarships by Term 2017-2025'[Amount Earned]), SUM('Athletic Scholarships by Term 2017-2025'[Amount Awarded]), 0) * 100

Name: Total Athletes Program
Expression: SUM('Participation Summary by Term and Sport'[Total Athletes])

Name: Average Career GPA Athletes
Expression: AVERAGE('Participation Summary by Term and Sport'[Average Career GPA])

Name: Academic Excellence Rate
Expression: DIVIDE(SUM('Academic Performance by Term Sport and Scholarship'[Students with GPA Above 3.5]), SUM('Academic Performance by Term Sport and Scholarship'[Total Students]), 0) * 100

Name: At-Risk Student Rate
Expression: DIVIDE(SUM('Academic Performance by Term Sport and Scholarship'[Students with GPA Below 2.5]), SUM('Academic Performance by Term Sport and Scholarship'[Total Students]), 0) * 100

Name: Program Completion Rate
Expression: DIVIDE(AVERAGE('Participation Summary by Term and Sport'[Average Hours Earned]), 120, 0) * 100

Name: Gender Diversity Index
Expression: 100 - ABS(DIVIDE(SUM('Participation Summary by Term and Sport'[Male Athletes]), SUM('Participation Summary by Term and Sport'[Female Athletes]), 0) - 1) * 50

Name: Projected Graduates
Expression: CALCULATE([Total Athletes Program], 'Participation Summary by Term and Sport'[Average Hours Earned] >= 90)

Name: High Performance Athletes
Expression: SUM('Academic Performance by Term Sport and Scholarship'[Students with GPA Above 3.5])

Name: Academic Success Trend
Expression: VAR CurrentGPA = [Average Career GPA Athletes] VAR PreviousGPA = CALCULATE([Average Career GPA Athletes], 'Participation Summary by Term and Sport'[Award Year] = MAX('Participation Summary by Term and Sport'[Award Year]) - 1) RETURN CurrentGPA - PreviousGPA

Name: VAR CurrentYear
Expression: SUM('Participation Summary by Term and Sport'[Total Athletes])

Name: Academic Risk Exposure
Expression: [At-Risk Student Rate] * [Total Athletic Investment] / 100

Name: Scholarship Default Risk
Expression: DIVIDE(COUNTROWS(FILTER('Athletic Scholarships by Term 2017-2025', 'Athletic Scholarships by Term 2017-2025'[Amount Earned] = 0)), COUNTROWS('Athletic Scholarships by Term 2017-2025'), 0) * 100

Name: Financial Concentration Risk
Expression: VAR MaxSportInvestment = MAXX(VALUES('Scholarship Summary by Term and Sport'[Sport Name]), [Total Athletic Investment]) RETURN DIVIDE(MaxSportInvestment, [Total Athletic Investment], 0) * 100

Name: Compliance Risk Score
Expression: ([At-Risk Student Rate] * 0.4) + ([Scholarship Default Risk] * 0.3) + ([Financial Concentration Risk] * 0.3)

Name: Retention Risk Factor
Expression: 100 - [Program Completion Rate]

Name: Investment at Risk
Expression: [Academic Risk Exposure] + ([Scholarship Default Risk] / 100 * [Total Athletic Investment])

Name: Performance Variance
Expression: STDEV.P('Participation Summary by Term and Sport'[Average Career GPA])

Name: Budget Overrun Risk
Expression: DIVIDE(COUNTROWS(FILTER('Athletic Scholarships by Term 2017-2025', 'Athletic Scholarships by Term 2017-2025'[Amount Awarded] > 'Athletic Scholarships by Term 2017-2025'[Amount Earned] * 1.1)), COUNTROWS('Athletic Scholarships by Term 2017-2025'), 0) * 100

Name: Operational Risk Index
Expression: ([Retention Risk Factor] * 0.5) + ([Performance Variance] * 20)

Name: Strategic Risk Rating
Expression: SWITCH(TRUE(), [Compliance Risk Score] <= 10, 1, [Compliance Risk Score] <= 25, 2, [Compliance Risk Score] <= 50, 3, [Compliance Risk Score] <= 75, 4, 5)

Name: Athletes per Dollar Invested
Expression: DIVIDE([Total Athletes Program], [Total Athletic Investment], 0) * 1000

Name: Average Investment per Athlete
Expression: DIVIDE([Total Athletic Investment], [Total Athletes Program], 0)

Name: Scholarship Utilization Rate
Expression: [Budget Efficiency Ratio] * 100

Name: Academic Output per Dollar
Expression: DIVIDE([Average Career GPA Athletes] * [Total Athletes Program], [Total Athletic Investment], 0) * 10000

Name: Cost Efficiency Index
Expression: DIVIDE([High Performance Athletes], [Total Athletic Investment], 0) * 100000

Name: Resource Allocation Score
Expression: 100 - ([Financial Concentration Risk] / 2)

Name: Performance to Cost Ratio
Expression: DIVIDE([Academic Excellence Rate], [Average Investment per Athlete], 0) * 1000

Name: Operational Leverage
Expression: DIVIDE([Total Athletes Program], [Total Scholarship Athletes], 0)

Name: Productivity Index
Expression: ([Academic Excellence Rate] / 100) * ([Scholarship Utilization Rate] / 100) * 100

Name: Efficiency Benchmark
Expression: DIVIDE([Athletes per Dollar Invested], 0.5, 0) * 100

Name: Overall Program Health
Expression: ([Academic Excellence Rate] * 0.3) + ([Scholarship Utilization Rate] * 0.3) + ([Gender Diversity Index] * 0.2) + (100 - [Strategic Risk Rating] * 20) * 0.2

Name: Investment ROI Percentage
Expression: DIVIDE([Academic Output per Dollar], 1, 0)

Name: Board Reporting Score
Expression: MIN([Overall Program Health], 100)

Name: Competitive Position
Expression: RANKX(ALL('Participation Summary by Term and Sport'[Sport Name]), [Average Career GPA Athletes], , DESC)

Name: Stakeholder Value Index
Expression: ([High Performance Athletes] / [Total Athletes Program] * 100) + ([Scholarship Yield Rate])

Name: Program Sustainability
Expression: 100 - ([Investment at Risk] / [Total Athletic Investment] * 100)
